{"text":"<BaseLayout title={entry.data.title} description={entry.data.description}>\n\t<div class=\"stack gap-20\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stack gap-15\">\n\t\t\t<header>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wrapper stack gap-2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"back-link\" href=\"/work/\"><Icon icon=\"arrow-left\" /> Work</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<Hero title={entry.data.title} align=\"start\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"details\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tags\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{entry.data.tags.map((t) => <Pill>{t}</Pill>)}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"description\">{entry.data.description}</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</Hero>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</header>\n\t\t\t<main class=\"wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"stack gap-10 content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t{entry.data.img && <img src={entry.data.img} alt={entry.data.img_alt || ''} />}\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<Content />\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</main>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<ContactCTA />\n\t</div>\n</BaseLayout>","source":"v4-astro-withastro-astro-examples-portfolio-src-pages-work-slug-astro-29-56-2759-0064","language":"astro","syntax_language":"astro","framework":"astro","project":"keyloop-corpus","level":"block","difficulty":"hard","score":12}
{"text":"<Layout title=\"Home\">\n\t<h1>Advanced Routing</h1>\n\t<p>\n\t\tThis example uses <code>src/app.ts</code> to control the request pipeline with Hono. Individual feature\n\t\tmiddleware from <code>astro/hono</code> and <code>astro/fetch</code>\n\t\tare composed together, with your own Hono middleware running between them.\n\t</p>\n\n\t<div class=\"cards\">\n\t\t<a href=\"/dashboard\" class=\"card\">\n\t\t\t<h2>Dashboard</h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Protected by auth middleware. You'll be redirected to login without a session cookie.</p>\n\t\t</a>\n\t\t<a href=\"/old-dashboard\" class=\"card\">\n\t\t\t<h2>Old Dashboard Link</h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Redirected by Astro's built-in routing inside <code>astro()</code>.</p>\n\t\t</a>\n\t\t<a href=\"/es\" class=\"card\">\n\t\t\t<h2>Spanish</h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Served through Astro's i18n handling, also composed inside <code>astro()</code>.</p>\n\t\t</a>\n\t</div>\n</Layout>","source":"v4-astro-withastro-astro-examples-advanced-routing-src-pages-index-astro-5-27-2705-0065","language":"astro","syntax_language":"astro","framework":"astro","project":"keyloop-corpus","level":"block","difficulty":"hard","score":11}
{"text":"<div class=\"not-content\">\n\t<div class=\"palette\">\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tAstro.props.light ? (\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"circle\" style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-accent)\" />\n\t\t\t) : (\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"circle\" style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-accent-high)\" />\n\t\t\t)\n\t\t}\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-black)\"></div>\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-white)\"></div>\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-gray-1)\"></div>\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-gray-2)\"></div>\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-gray-3)\"></div>\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-gray-4)\"></div>\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-gray-5)\"></div>\n\t\t<div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-gray-6)\"></div>\n\t\t{Astro.props.light && <div style=\"--bg:var(--sl-color-gray-7)\" />}\n\t</div>\n</div>","source":"v4-astro-withastro-starlight-docs-src-components-theme-designer-palette-astro-7-26-0023-0063","language":"astro","syntax_language":"astro","framework":"astro","project":"keyloop-corpus","level":"block","difficulty":"hard","score":13}
